high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the kitchen counter
Pick up the fork behind the bread loaf from the counter
Turn left and walk to the kitchen sink
Wash the fork under water in the sink then remove it
Turn around and walk across to the dark cabinet with the microwave on it
Put the fork down on the dark cabinet just left of the other fork
anns.task_desc: Put the washed fork on the dark cabinet

high_descs: Turn left for four steps, turn left for four steps and stop in front of the bread on the counter.
Pick up the fork on the counter near the wall behind the bread.
Turn left for six steps, turn right to face the sink.
Put her fork in the sink, turn on the water and fill the sink halfway, when the water drains, pick up the fork.
Turn right for seven steps, turn right for five steps and stop in front of the table with the microwave.
Put the fork on the table to the left of the existing fork and behind the front shaker, horizontally with the tines on the table and leaning against the front shaker.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean fork on table by microwave

high_descs: turn left, turn left, walk to the counter with a bread on it
grab the fork on the counter
turn left, walk to the sink
put the fork in the sink, wash the fork with water, take the fork out
turn right, walk to the microwave
put the fork by the microwave
anns.task_desc: wash the fork in the sink, put it by the microwave
